TITLE: Episode 35 - Waco pt. 1 of 3 The Sinful Messiah (MLGA recast)
DESCRIPTION: On today, the 27th anniversary of the slaughter of the Branch Davidians in Waco, Texas, I wanted to share the first of a three part miniseries about those events. It is a recast from the Make Liberty Great Again podcast. This will blow your mind.
